Energy Efficiency Action
The company has recently taken several steps to increase the businesses' energy efficiency across its chain of
autocentres, head office and in terms of the fleet.
With regards fleet, we have invested in one electric vehicle to date, trialling it's effectiveness for day to day operations. All
vehicles purchased are regularly serviced to minimise emissions.
