financial statements at 31 December 2019. The consolidated financial statements of NCR Corporation are
available publicly from 3097, Satellite Boulevard Building 800, Third Floor, Duluth, Georgia 30096, USA.
The company is exempt from disclosing related party transactions as they are with other companies that are
wholly owned within the NCR group.
